Codehesion is a South African software development company that produces world-class work for the biggest names in business. Its clients include multiple market leaders – from Woolworths and Leroy Merlin, to Peermont Global and Marcura, to Poynting and Nology. These businesses use Codehesion for its expertise in a range of areas, including custom software development, mobile application development, design, maintenance, project management, team augmentation, and training. To ensure it delivers excellent work to its clients, Codehesion only employs experienced and highly-skilled software engineers, computer scientists, and project managers who are specialists in their fields. The result is a long list of satisfied clients and Codehesion winning multiple awards for its work – including a 2022 MTN Business App of the Year Award and two awards at the 2021 Supersonic New Generation Social & Digital Media Awards. Codehesion offers a wide range of software development services to its clients – all of which are delivered by its highly-skilled experts. It also allows businesses to select how its development work is run. Clients can choose to: Whichever option is selected, Codehesion guarantees exceptional results. To make it easy for your company to work with Codehesion, it offers a free consultation process. This consultation will allow Codehesion to assess your requirements and provide insights into the scope of work required, the predicted timelines, and expected costs. For a risk-free consultation – Contact Codehesion here.